# Tuicraft Codebase Architecture

## 1. Overall Structure

The project is a WoW 3.3.5a chat client with two modes: an interactive TUI and a background daemon with IPC. The directory layout:

```
src/
  main.ts              - Entry point, dispatches CLI actions
  cli/                 - CLI parsing, IPC client, help text, setup wizard
  daemon/              - Daemon server, IPC command dispatch
  lib/                 - Shared utilities (config, paths, ring buffer, session log)
  ui/                  - TUI rendering, command parsing, formatters
  wow/                 - WoW protocol client
    client.ts          - Auth + world session, WorldHandle
    entity-store.ts    - Entity tracking store
    crypto/            - SRP auth, ARC4 encryption
    protocol/          - Packet parsing/building for every opcode area
  test/                - Test fixtures, mock servers, mock handle
```

